name: Cluster-Analysis-of-Online-Food-Delivery-Popularity-Through-Uber
description: Utilising clustering algorithms like Affinity Propagation, Gaussian Mixture Models, Spectral Clustering, Fuzzy C-means, and Hierarchical Clustering to reveal customer segments and patterns in Uber Eats USA data, generating practical suggestions and visual insights.

name: 3.Identifying-Clusters-Assuming-Circular-Particles-and-Quantifying-Cluster-Attributes
description: This Python script analyzes the data obtained from segmented images using clustering techniques and generates summary reports in an Excel format. It reads Excel files containing segmented image data (paricle centroid locations and their representative diameter), performs agglomerative clustering assuming circular particles, and outputs excel file
